messages.message: Hi England! Would you be down for an EF and to DMZ the Channel?
Hey Italy! Can we agree to DMZ Piedmont and the Western Med?

Hello France,
How do you feel about a Sealion opening? I think we can be quite successful and quickly eliminate England.
As well, I would like a DMZ of Bur if you are comfortable with that.
Hi France! Is there any way you can move your armies towards Iberia this year?
What do you think?
Hey Germany! I'd love to do a Sealion. Do you want to bounce or move elsewhere with Munich?
I would prefer a DMZ.
As long as we are on the same page, the sealion is successful.
That's the plan! Hopefully we can work together soon.
Sounds good! Will you be focusing on England then?

messages.message: Awesome. Will you be willing to let me have Belgium? I could use another fleet against England.
That's the plan for now.
Sorry about the move to the Channel, I hadn't heard back from you.
Great. Do you have any idea what Italy is doing?
Absolutely! England has not responded to me at all. Very frustrating.
Yeah me neither.
Belgium is yours.
I haven't heard from Italy.
Me neither

I wish Russia would talk to me...
He should have opened north.
I'm very concerned about Russia and Turkey working together here
Thanks. You should be able to get into the North Sea here.
Maybe. I think I will just secure my neutrals for now.
That's a scary alliance.
I would be concerned about a R/T.
